Using the angles in $\triangle PQS$, we have $\angle PQS + \angle QSP + \angle SPQ = 180^\circ$. Thus, $x^\circ+2y^\circ + (180^\circ - 3y^\circ) = 180^\circ$ or $x-y+180 = 180$ or $x=y$.

